replies.body:
A lot of shaco hate in this thread. I think shaco is undeserving of his reputation as a toxic champion. He has one escape, which is also his engage, and is countered by pink wards. People who say he can't be competitive are partially right, you'll never see him in LCS. But there are many shaco mains who have climbed to diamond, master, (and one challenger I can think of,) so saying he only works in low elo is just wrong. 

In a game today I got hate for my build, which was a tankier version so I wouldn't get one shot but still deal damage, I ended the game 14/4/17. It happens, you learn to live with it. I do well in most of my shaco games, but that one game you do poorly, expect to get raged at hard. It comes with playing the champion. 

Also, anyone who judges you based on a champion you play, is a moron and should be ignored. If you like Shaco, play him, he has a very determined fan base {{champion:35}}
